1) After building new server in RackSpace, ssh in as root: root@192.168.1.1

2) Add new user:
~# adduser username

3) Add new user to sudoers
~# visudo

Logout from root account and log back in as the new user

4) Install NGINX server
~# sudo apt-get update
~# sudo apt-get install nginx

Check that the NGINX installation was successful by going to IP address in browser

